Product ID: System generated numerical ID that represents your product. One product ID is equivalent to a product page. Variations share the same product page and hence they share the same Product ID.
Product Name: Product name should include product brand and model. Avoid irrelevant keywords as it may cause the listing to be banned.
Status: This indicates your product level status. Product will be active if one of variantion is active, will be inactive only if all variations are inactive.
